\begin_layout Subsection
Configuration and Continuity
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Each instance maintains:
 a stable UUID (generated on first run,
 never changed),
 a persona document,
 a character specification of formal normative propositions,
 and a session preamble template assembled from live memory state each cycle.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Memory Subsystem
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Nine append-only JSONL stores are indexed in ETS by the Librarian actor.
 Current state is derived by replaying operations chronologically—
no record is modified or deleted during normal operation.
\end_layout

