 and schemas—
is a git repository managed by a backup actor.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Periodic commits.

\series default
 The backup actor makes automatic git commits at a configurable interval (default 5
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

minutes).
 Each commit captures the complete agent state.
