\begin_layout Standard
Facts in the fact store have confidence scores that decay over time via a half-life formula:
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\text{confidence}_{t}=\text{confidence}_{0}\times2^{-\text{age\_days}/\text{half\_life\_days}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


