\begin_layout Standard
The combination of these properties means that many classes of bugs that are common in Python agent systems—
unhandled exceptions,
 race conditions on shared state,
 cascading failures from one component crash,
 missing message handlers after refactoring—
are either impossible or caught at compile time in Springdrift.
 This is not a theoretical advantage:
 over 23
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

days of continuous operation,
 the system's failure recovery was entirely automatic,
 and no data corruption was observed.
\end_layout

