\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

Do nothing.
\end_layout

\end_inset

 A single elevated reading is often noise.
 The readings are evidence,
 not directives.
 Equanimity includes the capacity to notice a state and continue without being compelled by it.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
What Is Excluded and Why
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
D
\begin_inset Formula $'$
\end_inset

